This is the Debian prepackaged version of GNU indent, a C language
source code formatting program. GNU indent was written by Joseph Arceneaux,
and it is currently maintained by David Ingamells.

This package was first put together by Bill Mitchell
<mitchell@mdd.comm.mot.com>.

It is currently maintained by Santiago Vila <sanvila@debian.org>.
The source for this release was taken from:

http://indent.isidore-it.eu/indent-2.2.11.tar.gz

